RUN |2 version=1.15.1 prog=samtools /bin/sh -c curl -L https://github.com/samtools/${prog}/releases/download/${version}/${prog}-${version}.tar.bz2 --output ${prog}.tar.bz2 &&   bunzip2 ${prog}.tar.bz2 &&   tar xf ${prog}.tar &&   cd ${prog}-${version} &&   ./configure --prefix=/usr/local &&   make &&   make install # buildkit
